==Equipment==

Activate [[Protect from Magic]], and be prepared to use [[Protect Item]] if [[4-iteming]]. Similar to the [[Chaos Elemental|chaos elemental]], he can unequip your items.  

'''Note:''' Ensure you are not risking more than you are willing to lose. 

It is recommended to use [[inventory blocking food]] as he cannot disarm you if there are no slots in your inventory for your weapons. Examples of this are [[Pies]], [[Curry]], and [[Stew]].

If you are using potions, it is advised to make sure that vial smashing is turned off. This option can be turned off in the settings menu under the gameplay section. [[Blighted super restore]] can be used, as it's in the [[Wilderness]].

Note that Ava's devices can be lost on death in Wilderness above level 20, so the assembler should only be brought if it is one of the player's protected items, or can be replaced easily. A [[Trouver parchment]] can be used to protect it — at a cost. Generally this isn't worth it for this activity. Instead, the player should only bring three or four valuable items, the rest of the gear being easily replaceable. 



