==Inventory ==

*2 [[divine ranging potion]].
*4–6 [[Blighted super restore|blighted super restores]].
*[[Looting bag]] (recommended).
*[[Ghorrock teleport]] (at least 2 as otherwise you will be left with an empty inventory space after you use the first one, and the boss would unequip your gear), [[runes]] for casting, or [[burning amulet]] (optional, as you can get to the boss via the Wilderness obelisk to the north).
*An emergency [[teleport]] (optional—only works in level 30 or 20 Wilderness or less. See [[Wilderness#Teleport_restrictions|Wilderness teleport restrictions]] for info).
*[[Summer pie]]s or [[Wild pie]]s are the best food to bring here, as they heal 22 per slot and leave the pie dish in the inventory, to counter the disarming ability of the chaos fanatic. Alternatively, [[Curry]] heals less (19 Hitpoints) but heals in one bite, whereas the pies are eaten in two bites healing 11 per bite.  

